Episode 14

3
00:02:21,440 --> 00:02:22,240
You wake up?

4
00:02:22,520 --> 00:02:23,240
OK.

5
00:02:23,360 --> 00:02:24,640
So it is around 5 a.m. in the morning now.

6
00:02:28,880 --> 00:02:30,640
For fear that you feels nervous without the headband.

7
00:02:31,000 --> 00:02:32,600
I put it on for you.

8
00:02:35,520 --> 00:02:37,160
I swam around at the bottom of the pond just now.

9
00:02:37,400 --> 00:02:40,040
I found that guy really smart.

10
00:02:40,520 --> 00:02:42,920
He would discover us within the time of burning a joss stick.

11
00:02:44,360 --> 00:02:46,120
I haven't found out the hole Jiang Cheng mentioned.

12
00:02:46,160 --> 00:02:46,960
I am afraid

13
00:02:47,360 --> 00:02:49,400
it has been plugged by the monster.

14
00:02:50,560 --> 00:02:51,320
With your wound

15
00:02:51,920 --> 00:02:53,160
you shouldn't go into the water.

16
00:02:55,440 --> 00:02:57,160
I'm not so delicate.

17
00:02:57,840 --> 00:02:58,560
But you.

18
00:02:58,840 --> 00:03:01,520
How is the effect of the medicine Wen Ning gave me?

19
00:03:05,880 --> 00:03:07,800
Jiang Cheng has left for so long.

20
00:03:07,920 --> 00:03:10,680
I don't know how long it will be before he find reinforcements.

21
00:03:11,240 --> 00:03:12,120
I guess

22
00:03:12,440 --> 00:03:13,600
we still have to stay here

23
00:03:13,680 --> 00:03:14,800
for a period of time

24
00:03:15,360 --> 00:03:16,640
And against the monster

25
00:03:17,000 --> 00:03:17,960
we still have a fight.

26
00:03:18,840 --> 00:03:19,880
What do you think

27
00:03:20,160 --> 00:03:20,920
the monster looks like?

28
00:03:21,080 --> 00:03:21,920
A turtle.

29
00:03:22,200 --> 00:03:23,280
A big turtle.

30
00:03:24,640 --> 00:03:25,760
There's a kind of mythic creature

31
00:03:26,040 --> 00:03:27,440
with the similar shape.

32
00:03:29,280 --> 00:03:30,640
Mythic creature?

33
00:03:33,400 --> 00:03:34,400
What you mentioned

34
00:03:34,560 --> 00:03:35,880
is the mythic creature Xuanwu, right?

35
00:03:36,280 --> 00:03:38,280
Xuanwu is also called Xuanming.

36
00:03:38,360 --> 00:03:40,080
The combination of tortoise and snake, kind of Water Immortal.

37
00:03:40,480 --> 00:03:41,280
Exactly.

38
00:03:43,800 --> 00:03:45,480
Is any mythic creature the same as this

39
00:03:45,600 --> 00:03:46,440
with a mouth filled with ugly tushes.

40
00:03:46,520 --> 00:03:47,480
And it even eats human.

41
00:03:48,240 --> 00:03:50,360
There's a big gap between the imagination and the reality!

42
00:03:51,520 --> 00:03:53,320
It is not the real mythic creature Xuanwu.

43
00:03:53,720 --> 00:03:54,560
But

44
00:03:55,120 --> 00:03:57,080
I have heard that there was a fake Xuanwu.

45
00:03:57,960 --> 00:03:59,240
It is similar to this monster.

46
00:03:59,440 --> 00:04:01,040
Fake Xuanwu.

47
00:04:02,750 --> 00:04:03,950
What is that?

48
00:04:04,560 --> 00:04:05,560
Do you still remember

49
00:04:06,200 --> 00:04:07,560
what Senior Lan Yi has mentioned before,

50
00:04:08,040 --> 00:04:09,400
the Slaughter Xuanwu.

51
00:04:11,880 --> 00:04:14,120
The Slaughter Xuanwu?

52
00:04:19,560 --> 00:04:22,200
Xue Chonghai manipulated an ancient mythic creature

53
00:04:22,200 --> 00:04:23,680
the Slaughter Xuanwu.

54
00:04:29,640 --> 00:04:30,600
Oh, I remember.

55
00:04:30,920 --> 00:04:31,920
As you mentioned

56
00:04:32,080 --> 00:04:34,120
it's something like this big turtle.

57
00:04:34,680 --> 00:04:35,680
Could it be that

58
00:04:35,960 --> 00:04:37,080
the big turtle

59
00:04:37,320 --> 00:04:39,440
is what Xue Chonghai left hundreds of years ago

60
00:04:39,480 --> 00:04:40,400
the Slaughter Xuanwu?

61
00:04:40,680 --> 00:04:41,760
That's right.

62
00:04:44,240 --> 00:04:45,400
Never mind.

63
00:04:45,720 --> 00:04:47,200
Whatever it is.

64
00:04:47,640 --> 00:04:50,000
We have said to be chivalrous and venture together.

65
00:04:50,160 --> 00:04:51,040
If today,

66
00:04:51,560 --> 00:04:53,640
we can kill the big turtle,

67
00:04:53,800 --> 00:04:55,520
then we are getting some chivalric fame for ourselves.

68
00:04:56,040 --> 00:04:58,920
Even if unfortunately we are killed by the monster

69
00:04:59,320 --> 00:05:03,080
it would be a death by the creature aged hundreds, thousands...

70
00:05:03,760 --> 00:05:04,760
No, no.

71
00:05:05,080 --> 00:05:07,400
A death by a big monster aged ten thousand years

72
00:05:07,760 --> 00:05:09,680
is not a shame even if people hear it, right?

73
00:07:06,400 --> 00:07:07,640
Killer-String.

74
00:07:07,680 --> 00:07:08,640
The instrument Qin has seven strings

75
00:07:08,760 --> 00:07:09,640
from thick to thin

76
00:07:09,800 --> 00:07:10,960
which can be split and combined.

77
00:07:11,600 --> 00:07:12,920
Cutting bones and meat like cutting mud.

78
00:07:13,120 --> 00:07:14,440
We can break through it from within.

79
00:07:15,400 --> 00:07:17,040
I agree to break through it from within.

80
00:07:17,400 --> 00:07:19,240
But the Killer-String of your Lan clan

81
00:07:19,400 --> 00:07:20,520
according to what I have heard

82
00:07:20,920 --> 00:07:22,920
is limited while in the turtle shell

83
00:07:23,200 --> 00:07:24,680
which can hamper your performance.

84
00:07:25,440 --> 00:07:28,080
Moreover due to your leg's wound

85
00:07:28,560 --> 00:07:31,440
the effect of the Killer-String will be greatly reduced.

86
00:07:32,080 --> 00:07:32,840
Listen to me.

87
00:07:53,320 --> 00:07:55,400
The turtle shell of Slaughter Xuanwu is solid as a fort.

88
00:07:55,560 --> 00:07:56,840
The scarfskin is extremely hard.

89
00:07:57,680 --> 00:07:59,240
It seems impossible to break.

90
00:07:59,640 --> 00:08:00,760
But the more so,

91
00:08:01,120 --> 00:08:03,280
the flesh part hiding in the shell

92
00:08:03,600 --> 00:08:05,240
is more likely to be fragile.

93
00:08:06,960 --> 00:08:08,720
I can creep in its turtle shell

94
00:08:09,440 --> 00:08:10,920
to find its weakness

95
00:08:11,720 --> 00:08:12,880
and focus on attacking it.

96
00:08:13,560 --> 00:08:14,880
Force it out of the turtle shell.

97
00:08:37,000 --> 00:08:38,480
Once it is out of the turtle shell,

98
00:08:38,840 --> 00:08:40,550
you can use the Killer-String.

99
00:08:41,280 --> 00:08:42,670
We collaborate from inside and outside

100
00:08:43,080 --> 00:08:44,400
and fight it to our last breath.

101
00:08:45,240 --> 00:08:47,200
Let's see who'd die first.

102
00:08:47,680 --> 00:08:48,560
Be careful.

103
00:09:16,720 --> 00:09:17,440
How's that?

104
00:09:17,720 --> 00:09:19,120
Luckily, you didn't get in.

105
00:09:19,520 --> 00:09:21,320
Even if the smell doesn't make you vomit,

106
00:09:21,550 --> 00:09:23,270
you'd faint from the stench.

107
00:10:59,560 --> 00:11:00,400
Lan Zhan.

108
00:11:01,320 --> 00:11:02,760
The monster is so horrible.

109
00:11:03,800 --> 00:11:05,280
It not only eats human flesh,

110
00:11:06,360 --> 00:11:08,560
but also digests the their spiritual cognition.

111
00:11:11,880 --> 00:11:12,920
Just like Yin Iron.

112
00:12:15,325 --> 00:12:16,565
The resentment is so strong.

113
00:12:19,120 --> 00:12:20,400
It seems that the sword

114
00:12:20,720 --> 00:12:22,680
gets the Slaughter Xuanwu stuck here.

115
00:13:29,760 --> 00:13:31,120
Lan Zhan.

116
00:15:47,320 --> 00:15:48,360
Wei Ying.

117
00:17:56,520 --> 00:17:57,960
Wei Ying. Wei Ying.

118
00:17:59,640 --> 00:18:01,280
Wake up. Wake up.

119
00:18:10,800 --> 00:18:11,840
Congratulations, father!

120
00:18:12,080 --> 00:18:13,360
The power of puppets is boosted.

121
00:18:13,480 --> 00:18:15,640
Unifying all main clans can be expected soon.

122
00:18:19,080 --> 00:18:21,160
Tell Wen Xu to find Xue Yang.

123
00:18:21,280 --> 00:18:22,040
And,

124
00:18:23,040 --> 00:18:24,040
if there is anyone

125
00:18:24,120 --> 00:18:25,640
concerned with Xue Yang near Yueyang and Qinghe,

126
00:18:25,640 --> 00:18:27,080
you should check it out.

127
00:18:27,240 --> 00:18:28,080
Yes.

128
00:18:29,120 --> 00:18:30,040
But father,

129
00:18:30,440 --> 00:18:32,160
I don't understand one thing.

130
00:18:32,920 --> 00:18:34,400
You have got three shards of Yin Iron.

131
00:18:34,400 --> 00:18:36,320
Why still search for the last one?

132
00:18:38,240 --> 00:18:40,120
As powerful as three shards are,

133
00:18:40,480 --> 00:18:41,600
never can those puppets be

134
00:18:42,080 --> 00:18:44,160
