135
00:18:44,400 --> 00:18:45,320
I see.

136
00:18:45,440 --> 00:18:47,080
In case that Xue Yang makes puppets at the same time,

137
00:18:47,160 --> 00:18:48,920
even if we have the power of the three shards of Yin Iron,

138
00:18:49,040 --> 00:18:50,680
