139
00:18:54,320 --> 00:18:55,480
I'm ready to get down to it.

140
00:18:56,800 --> 00:18:57,760
Go ahead.

141
00:19:19,040 --> 00:19:20,120
Is it dead?

142
00:19:20,360 --> 00:19:22,400
Lan Zhan, is it dead?

143
00:19:26,360 --> 00:19:27,320
Yes.

144
00:19:29,120 --> 00:19:30,440
Yes?

145
00:19:31,760 --> 00:19:32,880
