No.

153
00:20:16,800 --> 00:20:17,760
Little did I think before,

154
00:20:18,720 --> 00:20:20,240
one day in my life,

155
00:20:20,480 --> 00:20:23,640
I could see Second Childe Lan acting so concerned like this,

156
00:20:37,600 --> 00:20:38,480
Lan Zhan.

157
00:20:39,840 --> 00:20:43,800
I didn't think I could survive just now.

158
00:20:54,720 --> 00:20:55,320
Wei Ying.

159
00:20:56,200 --> 00:20:57,160
You got a fever.

160
00:21:20,040 --> 00:21:21,960
So comfortable, Lan Zhan.

161
00:21:49,400 --> 00:21:51,320
It's so boring.

162
00:21:55,400 --> 00:21:57,560
Why hasn't Jiang Cheng

163
00:21:57,880 --> 00:22:00,320
