00:24:55,560 --> 00:24:56,440
Pleasant to hear.

186
00:25:04,360 --> 00:25:05,400
Lan Zhan.

187
00:25:05,920 --> 00:25:10,240
What's the name of this song?

188
00:26:31,720 --> 00:26:32,360
Wei Wuxian.

189
00:26:32,360 --> 00:26:33,360
If you're awake, you just get up then.

190
00:26:35,720 --> 00:26:36,840
You are so heavy.

191
00:26:36,920 --> 00:26:38,440
Even the stone is lighter than you.

192
00:26:39,720 --> 00:26:40,880
It's you.

193
00:26:42,400 --> 00:26:43,320
Do not get me wrong.

194
00:26:43,640 --> 00:26:45,000
I'm not here for you.

195
00:26:47,480 --> 00:26:48,520
In this way

196
00:26:48,640 --> 00:26:50,400
I should thank you a lot.

197
00:26:55,440 --> 00:26:56,240
Wei Wuxian.

198
00:26:57,760 --> 00:26:58,560
You woke up?

199
00:26:59,080 --> 00:26:59,960
Jiang Cheng.

200
00:27:00,440 --> 00:27:01,240
Wei Wuxian.

201
00:27:01,440 --> 00:27:02,720
You're finally awake.

202
00:27:06,120 --> 00:27:06,920
Jiang Cheng.

203
00:27:07,280 --> 00:27:09,240
Here you are at last!

204
00:27:09,800 --> 00:27:11,080
It's been many days since you escaped.

205
00:27:13,840 --> 00:27:14,600
How about Lan Zhan?

206
00:27:15,880 --> 00:27:16,640
He has left.

207
00:27:18,720 --> 00:27:19,720
He has left?

208
00:27:19,960 --> 00:27:21,360
He's still injured.

209
00:27:21,680 --> 00:27:23,080
Who hasn't got any injuries yet?

210
00:27:23,160 --> 00:27:24,800
Now Lan clan of Gusu is in a mess.

211
00:27:24,920 --> 00:27:26,280
He went back first by himself.

212
00:27:27,920 --> 00:27:29,080
Then he...

213
00:27:29,280 --> 00:27:30,120
Wei Wuxian!

214
00:27:30,320 --> 00:27:31,560
Why don't you thank me first?

215
00:27:31,840 --> 00:27:33,160
Do you know that in order to save you,

216
00:27:33,320 --> 00:27:34,600
Childe Jin and I hurried on with our journey

217
00:27:34,680 --> 00:27:36,520
even without our eyes closed for seven days!

218
00:27:43,560 --> 00:27:44,720
Seven days?

219
00:27:45,320 --> 00:27:46,280
It's been that long?

220
00:27:46,840 --> 00:27:47,640
Exactly.

221
00:27:47,880 --> 00:27:49,640
The nearest Gusu and Qinghe

222
00:27:49,760 --> 00:27:50,840
were all occupied by Wen clan.

223
00:27:51,040 --> 00:27:52,560
All of us have to go to Lanling first.

224
00:27:52,760 --> 00:27:55,920
But this time, we should thank Childe Jin.

225
00:27:56,840 --> 00:27:58,560
If Childe Jin hadn't persuaded Clan Leader Jin.

226
00:27:58,680 --> 00:27:59,560
into advocating

227
00:27:59,680 --> 00:28:00,840
to fight against Wen clan,

228
00:28:00,960 --> 00:28:02,520
we couldn't have brought anyone to save you.

229
00:28:03,600 --> 00:28:04,640
I don't have a sword.

230
00:28:05,520 --> 00:28:06,800
If I had chose to return to Yunmeng,

231
00:28:06,880 --> 00:28:08,200
it would be more than seven days.

232
00:28:09,560 --> 00:28:12,080
Yeah, I forgot that you all couldn't maneuver the sword.

233
00:28:16,480 --> 00:28:17,320
How about Wen Chao?

234
00:28:17,720 --> 00:28:18,720
How about his group?

235
00:28:19,040 --> 00:28:20,320
Didn't they stop you?

236
00:28:21,600 --> 00:28:22,640
Strange to say,

237
00:28:22,880 --> 00:28:24,760
I don't know what's happening to Wen clan recently.

238
00:28:25,160 --> 00:28:26,800
Wen Chao and Wen Xu were all sent out.

239
00:28:27,040 --> 00:28:28,400
It seems that they are looking for something.

240
00:28:30,000 --> 00:28:32,120
Otherwise, how could we dig the hole

241
00:28:32,200 --> 00:28:33,480
and save you out from the cave so easily?

242
00:28:46,760 --> 00:28:47,760
Anyway,

243
00:28:48,720 --> 00:28:50,480
this time you saved us.

244
00:28:53,280 --> 00:28:54,040
Thank you very much.

245
00:29:01,720 --> 00:29:02,440
Childe Jiang.

246
00:29:03,240 --> 00:29:04,320
Now that they have been rescued,

247
00:29:04,440 --> 00:29:06,240
let's get out of here.

248
00:29:06,680 --> 00:29:07,640
Now, the situation of other clans

249
00:29:07,680 --> 00:29:09,520
joining forces to fight against Wen clan has been decided.

250
00:29:10,160 --> 00:29:12,160
Other survived disciples have gathered in Lanling.

251
00:29:12,880 --> 00:29:14,760
Maybe this will attract Wen Ruohan’s attention.

252
00:29:16,000 --> 00:29:17,360
