254
00:29:20,400 --> 00:29:22,080
Wei Wuxian and I will rush back as soon as possible

255
00:29:22,200 --> 00:29:23,000
to persuade my father

256
00:29:23,200 --> 00:29:25,720
to discuss how to suppress Wen clan together.

257
00:29:26,160 --> 00:29:26,800
Great.

258
00:29:27,200 --> 00:29:28,320
Let's separate here.

259
00:29:30,800 --> 00:29:31,720
Take care.

260
00:29:41,960 --> 00:29:43,560
Unexpectedly,

261
00:29:44,360 --> 00:29:45,520
Jin Zixuan is really responsible.

262
00:29:46,320 --> 00:29:47,120
Let's go.

263
00:30:06,120 --> 00:30:08,040
Wei Wuxian, come on.

264
00:30:24,360 --> 00:30:25,280
Second Childe Wen.

265
00:30:25,800 --> 00:30:26,880
Someone just reported

266
00:30:27,040 --> 00:30:27,680
that...

267
00:30:27,880 --> 00:30:28,800
Say it!

268
00:30:29,640 --> 00:30:30,440
That someone had seen

269
00:30:30,560 --> 00:30:32,320
two Childes of Jing and Jiang

270
00:30:32,640 --> 00:30:35,400
bringing a dozen people and going into Mount Muxi.

271
00:30:35,520 --> 00:30:36,360
They...

272
00:30:37,080 --> 00:30:38,280
