276
00:30:46,440 --> 00:30:49,680
I think they're here to claim Wei Wuxian's dead body.

277
00:30:52,760 --> 00:30:53,640
You two.

278
00:30:53,720 --> 00:30:56,440
Go to the cave and have a look at Lan Wangji and Wei Wuxian

279
00:30:56,440 --> 00:30:57,920
