341
00:35:41,840 --> 00:35:42,640
Uncle Jiang,

342
00:35:42,960 --> 00:35:44,080
I'm actually okay.

343
00:35:44,280 --> 00:35:46,600
I just stayed in that cave for a few days.

344
00:35:50,800 --> 00:35:53,240
But it was Jiang Cheng these days

345
00:35:53,480 --> 00:35:55,160
