352
00:36:19,840 --> 00:36:21,280
You'd also be able to chat with me

353
00:36:21,840 --> 00:36:23,680
and chase the boredom away.

354
00:36:24,400 --> 00:36:25,320
Good Heavens,

355
00:36:25,400 --> 00:36:27,120
sitting face-to-face with Lan Zhan these days

356
00:36:27,280 --> 00:36:28,680
almost bored me to death.

357
00:36:29,200 --> 00:36:30,200
It served you right to be bored to death.

358
00:36:30,280 --> 00:36:31,520
You shouldn't have played the hero back then,

359
00:36:31,600 --> 00:36:32,720
and shouldn't have cared for such hot potato.

360
00:36:32,880 --> 00:36:33,680
If in the beginning you didn't...

361
00:36:33,760 --> 00:36:34,600
Jiang Cheng.

362
00:36:36,600 --> 00:36:39,560
