375
00:37:13,960 --> 00:37:15,720
“To try what shouldn't be tried ”

376
00:37:15,840 --> 00:37:17,520
is exactly how he is, isn't it?

377
00:37:17,680 --> 00:37:19,680
Fooling around even though he knew that

378
00:37:19,840 --> 00:37:21,000
it'd bring trouble to his clan?!

379
00:37:22,760 --> 00:37:23,600
What are you doing here?

380
00:37:24,920 --> 00:37:25,880
What a joke that

381
00:37:26,640 --> 00:37:28,200
