382
00:37:28,320 --> 00:37:29,320
Clan Leader Jiang,

383
00:37:29,840 --> 00:37:31,120
do you still remember

384
00:37:31,200 --> 00:37:33,120
that I'm also the host of Lotus Cove?

385
00:37:33,280 --> 00:37:34,200
Do you still remember

386
00:37:34,320 --> 00:37:37,600
that every inch of earth here is my territory?

387
00:37:37,960 --> 00:37:38,920
Do you still remember,

388
00:37:39,040 --> 00:37:40,320
between the one lying and the one standing,

389
00:37:40,360 --> 00:37:41,320
which one is your son?

390
00:37:41,320 --> 00:37:42,640
Of course I do.

391
00:37:44,240 --> 00:37:45,360
You do remember

392
00:37:45,680 --> 00:37:47,720
but there's no use if you simply remember.

393
00:37:51,680 --> 00:37:53,040
Wei Ying, you really can't take it

394
00:37:53,240 --> 00:37:55,440
unless he stirs up some trouble for even one day, can you?

395
00:37:55,800 --> 00:37:56,640
If I had known that,

396
00:37:56,875 --> 00:37:58,250
I would've made him stay in Lotus Cove properly

397
00:37:58,250 --> 00:37:59,250
and not go outside.

398
00:37:59,760 --> 00:38:00,680
Could Wen Chao

399
00:38:00,920 --> 00:38:02,920
really have dared to

400
00:38:02,920 --> 00:38:04,480
do anything to the two young Childes

401
00:38:04,560 --> 00:38:05,440
of Lan and Jin?

402
00:38:05,760 --> 00:38:07,080
