403
00:38:07,360 --> 00:38:08,880
it'd mean that they ran out of luck.

404
00:38:09,320 --> 00:38:11,080
Since when was it your turn to play the hero?

405
00:38:11,480 --> 00:38:12,920
I'm saying this right now.

406
00:38:13,520 --> 00:38:14,560
You can just wait and see.

407
00:38:15,120 --> 00:38:16,200
One day,

408
00:38:16,280 --> 00:38:17,920
