409
00:38:18,000 --> 00:38:18,880
Enough!

410
00:38:20,240 --> 00:38:21,360
Let's talk when we get back.

411
00:38:21,400 --> 00:38:22,360
Talk about what?

412
00:38:22,480 --> 00:38:23,560
Get back to where?

413
00:38:24,560 --> 00:38:26,040
I'll talk here and now.

414
00:38:26,520 --> 00:38:28,160
I have nothing to be ashamed of, anyways!

415
00:38:28,680 --> 00:38:29,920
Jiang Cheng, come over here.

416
00:38:35,840 --> 00:38:36,720
Clan Leader Jiang,

417
00:38:37,040 --> 00:38:38,880
it seems that there are some things I have to say.

418
00:38:39,160 --> 00:38:40,560
Look carefully,

419
00:38:40,760 --> 00:38:42,600
this, is your own son,

420
00:38:42,800 --> 00:38:44,440
the future leader of Lotus Cove.

421
00:38:44,880 --> 00:38:45,530
Even if you frown upon him

422
00:38:45,640 --> 00:38:47,680
just because I was the one who gave birth to him,

423
00:38:48,160 --> 00:38:49,680
his surname is still Jiang!

424
00:38:50,680 --> 00:38:52,000
I don't believe that you haven't heard of

425
00:38:52,080 --> 00:38:54,040
how the outside people gossip

426
00:38:54,360 --> 00:38:56,120
that Clan Leader Jiang has still not moved on from

427
00:38:56,200 --> 00:38:58,640
a certain Wanderer though so many years have passed,

428
00:38:58,760 --> 00:39:00,720
regarding the son of his old friend as a son of his own.

429
00:39:01,160 --> 00:39:02,280
They're speculating

430
00:39:02,880 --> 00:39:04,560
if Wei Ying is your...

431
00:39:04,680 --> 00:39:05,560
Yu Ziyuan!

432
00:39:06,400 --> 00:39:07,280
Jiang Fengmian!

433
00:39:07,560 --> 00:39:08,650
Do you think that anything will change

434
00:39:08,650 --> 00:39:09,475
just because you raised your voice?!

435
00:39:10,160 --> 00:39:11,560
Do you think that I don't know you?!

436
00:39:12,440 --> 00:39:13,120
You!

437
00:39:14,760 --> 00:39:15,600
Stop!

438
00:39:15,680 --> 00:39:16,640
I haven't finished yet.

439
00:39:35,360 --> 00:39:36,160
Jiang Cheng!

440
00:39:37,320 --> 00:39:38,320
Jiang Cheng!

441
00:39:39,840 --> 00:39:41,040
Jiang Cheng!

442
00:39:41,760 --> 00:39:42,800
Answer me if you heard me!

443
00:39:42,880 --> 00:39:43,800
Are you looking for a fight?!

444
00:39:46,680 --> 00:39:48,200
Go back to your bed and lie down properly!

445
00:39:49,680 --> 00:39:50,760
I can't do that,

446
00:39:50,880 --> 00:39:52,160
we need to get things straight!

447
00:39:52,280 --> 00:39:53,560
You really mustn't listen to that nonsense.

448
00:39:54,120 --> 00:39:55,720
What nonsense?

449
00:39:55,840 --> 00:39:58,360
Those things would dirty my mouth if I should say them.

450
00:39:58,600 --> 00:39:59,680
Wait for me!

451
00:40:00,600 --> 00:40:01,280
Anyway,

452
00:40:01,440 --> 00:40:03,120
both my parents are real people in this world.

453
00:40:03,480 --> 00:40:04,440
I don't want others

454
00:40:04,520 --> 00:40:06,160
assigning me to other households!

455
00:40:06,600 --> 00:40:07,560
Listen!

456
00:40:08,480 --> 00:40:10,040
Let's be honest,

457
00:40:10,200 --> 00:40:11,840
don't hide things so sulkily in your heart.

458
00:40:12,360 --> 00:40:13,080
You're...

459
00:40:13,240 --> 00:40:14,720
Uncle Jiang's own son,

460
00:40:15,000 --> 00:40:16,320
the future leader of Jiang clan.

461
00:40:16,840 --> 00:40:18,280
Of course Uncle Jiang

462
00:40:18,360 --> 00:40:19,640
would be stricter towards you.

463
00:40:20,480 --> 00:40:22,000
But I'm different.

464
00:40:22,440 --> 00:40:23,960
I'm the son of someone else.

465
00:40:24,120 --> 00:40:26,680
Both of my parents are good friends of Uncle Jiang.

466
00:40:26,840 --> 00:40:28,000
Of course,

467
00:40:28,120 --> 00:40:29,680
he'd cut me more slack.

468
00:40:30,320 --> 00:40:32,680
Such a reason you do understand, don't you?

469
00:40:32,960 --> 00:40:34,120
He's not strict towards me.

470
00:40:34,240 --> 00:40:35,320
He just doesn't like me.

471
00:40:38,040 --> 00:40:40,600
How can there be anyone who doesn't like his own son?

472
00:40:42,000 --> 00:40:43,120
Stop thinking such things!

473
00:40:43,240 --> 00:40:44,560
Those who have loose mouths,

474
00:40:44,640 --> 00:40:45,800
I'll beat them up on the encounter,

475
00:40:45,920 --> 00:40:47,280
so hard that even their mothers couldn't recognize them.

476
00:40:47,400 --> 00:40:48,320
There is, though.

477
00:40:48,520 --> 00:40:49,600
He doesn't like my mom

478
00:40:49,680 --> 00:40:50,800
and so he doesn't like me either.

479
00:40:53,240 --> 00:40:54,040
I know.

480
00:40:54,840 --> 00:40:56,320
I know that I don't have the personality he likes,

481
00:40:56,680 --> 00:40:58,080
and that I'm not the heir he wants.

482
00:40:58,560 --> 00:41:00,400
He thinks that I don't understand the motto of Jiang clan

483
00:41:00,760 --> 00:41:02,040
and that I don't have the air of Jiang clan in me.

484
00:41:02,040 --> 00:41:02,720
Those are all true!

485
00:41:02,960 --> 00:41:04,880
You killed the Slaughter Xuanwu together with Lan Wangji

486
00:41:05,000 --> 00:41:05,640
bathing in blood!

487
00:41:05,720 --> 00:41:06,480
How great that is.

488
00:41:06,800 --> 00:41:07,880
But what about me?

489
00:41:11,160 --> 00:41:12,280
I had also been running around for days

490
00:41:12,440 --> 00:41:13,480
completely exhausted

491
00:41:13,760 --> 00:41:14,960
with not one second of rest!

492
00:41:17,520 --> 00:41:19,240
The motto is of nothing.

493
00:41:19,920 --> 00:41:21,000
I'm telling you.

494
00:41:21,120 --> 00:41:23,800
Do you have to follow it just because it's a motto?

495
00:41:24,280 --> 00:41:25,575
Look at the principles of Lan clan of Gusu,

496
00:41:25,575 --> 00:41:26,825
there are over three thousand.

497
00:41:27,280 --> 00:41:28,760
If people followed every single one of them,

498
00:41:28,880 --> 00:41:29,920
would they even be alive at that point?

499
00:41:30,600 --> 00:41:31,680
And

500
00:41:31,880 --> 00:41:34,120
who said that being a clan leader means

501
00:41:34,240 --> 00:41:36,200
you have to go along with the style of the clan?

502
00:41:36,400 --> 00:41:37,200
I don't believe

503
00:41:37,280 --> 00:41:39,000
that so many clan leaders in Jiang clan

504
00:41:39,160 --> 00:41:40,320
were all the same.

505
00:41:41,920 --> 00:41:42,840
Even

506
00:41:43,240 --> 00:41:44,200
Lan clan of Gusu

507
00:41:44,320 --> 00:41:46,120
had a mutant like Lan Yi,

508
00:41:46,480 --> 00:41:48,440
but who could deny her position and her abilities?

509
00:41:48,880 --> 00:41:50,720
When talking about the famous gentry of Lan clan,

510
00:41:50,840 --> 00:41:51,840
who could skip over her?

511
00:41:51,960 --> 00:41:53,680
Who could skip over her Killer-String?

512
00:42:01,640 --> 00:42:02,720
So...

513
00:42:02,840 --> 00:42:04,040
just don't think about it.

514
00:42:04,440 --> 00:42:06,160
In the future, you'll be the clan leader

515
00:42:07,040 --> 00:42:08,360
and I'll be your subordinate

516
00:42:08,480 --> 00:42:10,200
like your father and my father.

517
00:42:11,480 --> 00:42:13,040
So if Lan clan of Gusu has its Jade Twin?

518
00:42:13,240 --> 00:42:14,960
Jiang clan of Yunmeng will have its Pride Twin!

519
00:42:15,280 --> 00:42:16,040
So,

520
00:42:16,560 --> 00:42:18,000
no one can say you don't deserve.

521
00:42:18,160 --> 00:42:18,880
Got it?

522
00:42:19,640 --> 00:42:20,720
Even yourself.

523
00:42:20,800 --> 00:42:23,040
If there were someone who says, I'd beat him hard.

524
00:42:23,120 --> 00:42:24,080
Look at yourself now.

525
00:42:24,160 --> 00:42:25,240
Who can you beat up?

526
00:42:28,160 --> 00:42:29,200
Jiang Cheng!

527
00:42:29,560 --> 00:42:30,560
You're hurting so much now,

528
00:42:30,680 --> 00:42:31,880
but why did you play the hero back then?!

529
00:42:32,120 --> 00:42:32,800
Serves you right!

530
00:42:32,960 --> 00:42:33,840
Teaches you a lesson!

531
00:42:33,920 --> 00:42:35,160
Was I playing the hero?!

532
00:42:35,240 --> 00:42:36,560
I had no other choice then!

533
00:42:46,800 --> 00:42:47,720
Jiang Cheng.

534
00:42:49,600 --> 00:42:51,400
Do you think we'll meet them again?

535
00:42:53,600 --> 00:42:54,720
How do I know?

